Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.82,0:00:44.19,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}眼差し　キラキラ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.28,0:00:52.43,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}あまり大きくない道でもいいね
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.55,0:00:56.97,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}そして　駆け出す　飛び込む　奇跡へ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.10,0:01:00.89,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}見上げる　手を振る　光へ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.93,0:01:05.69,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}止まらない気持ちを繋いで行く
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.61,0:01:08.53,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}リフレクティア
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.74,0:01:12.50,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}揺らめく　近付く　明日へ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.54,0:01:16.34,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}奏でる　夢見る　未来へ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.34,0:01:21.82,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}まっさらな空　どこまでも連れて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.07,0:01:27.17,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}涙の終わり　合図に
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.15,0:00:09.66,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}七彩的回路中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.07,0:00:13.55,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}那無數的話語
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.82,0:00:17.13,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}哪怕只是一點點
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.38,0:00:21.88,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}如果在這裡  我就能前進
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.65,0:00:25.06,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}突如其來的旋律
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.39,0:00:29.19,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}又令我心跳加速
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.32,0:00:37.51,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}揪住心扉  一點陰影也無法消除
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.82,0:00:44.19,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}你的眼神閃閃發光
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.28,0:00:52.43,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}就算不是太寬的道路也無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.55,0:00:56.97,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}於是  我向著奇跡衝出去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.10,0:01:00.89,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}抬頭仰望  向著光芒揮手
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.93,0:01:05.69,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}緊緊聯繫著無法停止的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.61,0:01:08.53,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Reflect  tear
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.74,0:01:12.50,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}猶豫著靠近明天
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.54,0:01:16.34,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}奏響夢幻的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.34,0:01:21.82,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}帶我去到嶄新藍天的任何一個角落
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.07,0:01:27.17,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}作為淚水終結的信號
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.25,0:22:32.52,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}叶わない願いごと　持て余して
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.69,0:22:39.70,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}歩き出す　くちびる歌いながら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.05,0:22:44.73,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}残された気持ちへと
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.11,0:22:49.49,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}冷たい雨降りかかる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.68,0:22:54.55,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}忘れたいと　忘れないと
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.87,0:22:59.24,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}ゆらゆら廻りながら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.66,0:23:04.33,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}沈む心　ワザと君に
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.29,0:23:08.24,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}I'm tellin' a lie
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.31,0:23:14.58,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}形のない二人だがらこそ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.09,0:23:18.02,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}大事にしたのに
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.08,0:23:19.73,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}訊きたい…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.73,0:23:27.33,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}今ここで何もかも話したら
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.46,0:23:32.98,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}変わるのですか？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.25,0:22:32.52,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}遙遠的心願  難以釋懷
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.69,0:22:39.70,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}唇邊的小調  伴我前行
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.05,0:22:44.73,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}胸中殘留的這份感情
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.11,0:22:49.49,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}被冰冷的雨水淋濕
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.68,0:22:54.55,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}想要忘記  無法忘記
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.87,0:22:59.24,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}想來想去  無法決定
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.66,0:23:04.33,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}沉寂的心  故意對你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.29,0:23:08.24,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}道出一句謊言
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.31,0:23:14.58,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}正因為我們不會有結果
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.09,0:23:18.02,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}所以對你才倍加珍惜
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.08,0:23:19.73,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}我想問…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.73,0:23:27.33,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}假如此時此地我全都告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.46,0:23:32.98,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}結局可會改變？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.83,0:01:39.45,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,1000)\pos(480,210)}2話  我…想做什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.53,0:23:55.02,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(480,160)}3話  怎麼了？  前幾天的事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.03,0:01:55.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}真一郎的鞋底也有蟑螂…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.29,0:01:55.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真堅強啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.82,0:02:01.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很疼愛它吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.44,0:02:03.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而你…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.38,0:02:17.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很傷心  非常地非常地傷心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.85,0:02:21.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石動乃繪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.07,0:02:32.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把眼淚送出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.88,0:02:43.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我說這件事的  仲上真一郎你是頭一個
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.01,0:02:46.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然對你說了  就必須得讓你相信
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.40,0:02:49.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相信…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.92,0:02:50.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.67,0:02:53.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼淚是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.94,0:02:56.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為那是悲傷的時候才…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.20,0:03:00.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是問那個
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.35,0:03:01.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼淚是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.98,0:03:06.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了清洗和濕潤眼球
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.03,0:03:08.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從淚腺分泌出來的…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.24,0:03:10.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很有前途
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.18,0:03:11.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.46,0:03:25.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有著一個使命
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.38,0:03:30.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我必須取回眼淚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.53,0:03:35.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為此  我需要被選中者的眼淚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.38,0:03:42.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  難不成…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.13,0:03:45.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然雷轟丸死於非命
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.46,0:03:49.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過它的確給我留下了後繼者
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.34,0:03:52.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這件事是我們兩人的秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.70,0:03:56.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是說出去的話  我的腦袋就不保了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.88,0:03:59.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說句話啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.09,0:04:07.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想如果是你的話  應該會相信我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.29,0:04:10.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.56,0:04:11.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天學校見
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.52,0:04:22.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經相信了嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.09,0:04:28.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再來一碗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.17,0:04:29.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.00,0:04:32.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要多吃點啊  阿真
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.46,0:04:35.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的米和平時是不同的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.63,0:04:39.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  你怎麼想的  決定了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.48,0:04:42.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.94,0:04:45.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最終擇校志願是什麼時候提交
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.60,0:04:48.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次我會問清楚的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.09,0:04:49.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.90,0:04:53.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  阿真  關於昨天那件事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.04,0:05:03.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我吃飽了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.85,0:05:04.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我倒杯茶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.22,0:05:05.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.06,0:05:10.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真是孩子氣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.83,0:05:13.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算老媽沒有反對…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.33,0:05:16.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的作品本來就沒被採用
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.13,0:05:25.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是把眼淚給那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.23,0:05:27.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我會變成什麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.20,0:05:29.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然會變得無法哭泣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.25,0:05:34.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無所謂了  那種事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.19,0:06:18.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的便當還是那麼不合時宜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.90,0:06:23.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要是想要的話  我隨時都可以跟你換
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.32,0:06:28.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,充滿了母愛的便當能那麼輕易就交換嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.46,0:06:32.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  作為點心的香蕉我就收下了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.62,0:06:37.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老媽把一根香蕉附在便當上交給我到底在想些什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.17,0:06:39.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說她很關心你咯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.78,0:06:48.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙就算在學校也是個怪人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.01,0:06:53.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在公眾面前對你那樣示愛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.97,0:06:56.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算你厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.41,0:06:59.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把掉地上的煎雞蛋撿起來吃的傢伙更厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.21,0:07:02.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不僅和湯淺比呂美同居
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.32,0:07:05.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像還被石動乃繪給迷上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.30,0:07:07.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼只有你這傢伙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.40,0:07:10.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且吃的還是別人便當裡的菜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.53,0:07:13.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲  帥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.12,0:07:34.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.70,0:07:40.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.32,0:07:43.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.65,0:07:47.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是  這個…是鳥的餌食吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.80,0:07:48.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不要嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.24,0:07:51.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.96,0:07:54.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很喜歡仰望真一郎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.38,0:08:02.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你就像在離天空很近的地方一樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.97,0:08:10.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的想讓我代替雷轟丸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.66,0:08:22.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.02,0:08:24.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被搶走也沒關係嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.46,0:08:30.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為住在同一屋簷下  所以就安心了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.46,0:08:33.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和真一郎君不是那種關係
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.02,0:08:38.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是不是觸動心弦了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.48,0:09:42.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我聽說前幾天這裡的雞被狸貓襲擊了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.71,0:09:47.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個墓是雞的…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.98,0:09:48.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷轟丸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.76,0:09:51.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是  墳墓的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.65,0:09:53.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟裡面還有一隻
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.97,0:10:04.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.37,0:10:13.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害  比呂美  你們已經正面交鋒了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.66,0:10:14.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是那樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.54,0:10:18.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.11,0:10:20.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷轟丸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.70,0:10:21.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…之墓？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.59,0:10:24.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是雞棚嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.60,0:10:27.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為裡面還有嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.78,0:10:49.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.15,0:10:51.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又要拿什麼來…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.96,0:11:00.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真一郎君  原來你認識她啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.05,0:11:03.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石動乃繪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.71,0:11:08.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道她有很多奇怪的傳聞嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.57,0:11:11.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我從野伏那聽到過
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.01,0:11:12.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.97,0:11:14.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和地底人是郵件朋友之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.90,0:11:16.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是愚蠢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.06,0:11:22.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說她一放學就爬上樹向恰巧路過的男生搭訕？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.26,0:11:30.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我透過瓶子對著太陽光
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.28,0:11:33.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凝視著裡面閃閃發光的液體
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.46,0:11:35.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.03,0:11:37.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,周圍一下子變暗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.23,0:11:39.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我突然睜開眼睛…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.35,0:11:46.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和地底人是郵件朋友的話我還是相信她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.66,0:11:51.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就當作沒有代替雞被搭訕這回事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.46,0:12:03.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.25,0:12:04.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.82,0:12:05.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好  阿真
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.08,0:12:07.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.67,0:12:18.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我吃飽了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.34,0:12:33.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我出門了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.97,0:12:50.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也最好快點吃完吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.56,0:13:09.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有事拜託你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.12,0:13:35.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  等了很久了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.62,0:13:43.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什  什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.54,0:13:45.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可疑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.10,0:13:48.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請來兩份白餅
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.99,0:13:49.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.29,0:13:54.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  可以說給我聽聽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.64,0:13:56.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個什麼請求
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.04,0:14:02.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說了  好像是希望我介紹石動乃繪給她認識
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.34,0:14:03.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.75,0:14:06.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我說幾次啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.33,0:14:11.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比呂美希望我介紹石動乃繪給她認識
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.43,0:14:14.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.99,0:14:18.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為比呂美想和她交朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.27,0:14:22.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不快點吃的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.86,0:14:25.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本店美味的今川燒就要涼掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.77,0:14:30.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得你還是再考慮一下何為待客之道比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.11,0:14:40.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是  湯淺同學她會有那種興趣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.86,0:14:43.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,興趣？  什麼興趣啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.69,0:14:46.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她應該更…  怎麼說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.52,0:14:48.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該說是正統派呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.61,0:14:51.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  作為旁人看來挺享受這倒是不錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.04,0:14:52.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這色色的…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.82,0:14:55.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說了  你倒是說說看那是什麼樣的興趣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.21,0:14:58.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸好  我女朋友的取向很正常
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.13,0:15:00.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧  小愛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.96,0:15:08.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是傻瓜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.23,0:15:41.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很高興啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.47,0:15:43.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不是高興
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.57,0:15:46.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟發生了令人悲傷的事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.98,0:15:47.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.69,0:15:52.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,充滿絕望的深邃黑暗的前方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.63,0:15:55.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看到了閃爍的光輝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.16,0:16:01.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我見到樹上的石動乃繪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.27,0:16:04.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雞被狸貓襲擊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.13,0:16:06.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得到紅果
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.09,0:16:08.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比呂美和我打招呼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.84,0:16:11.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上和她對視
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.46,0:16:13.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蟑螂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.51,0:16:16.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蟑螂…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.09,0:16:24.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真一郎的鞋底也有蟑螂…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.88,0:16:32.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被偽裝成天使的怪物關在了瓶子裡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.95,0:16:34.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走投無路的我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.69,0:16:37.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看到旁邊的瓶子裡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.42,0:16:43.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有和我一樣被關起來的  正在哭泣的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.54,0:16:50.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.73,0:16:53.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果要奪走別人眼淚的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.92,0:16:56.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就不該是我的  而是比呂美的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.42,0:17:28.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到你很受歡迎啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.35,0:17:33.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人想和你交朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.89,0:17:34.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我介紹給你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.01,0:17:35.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼時候可以呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.62,0:17:37.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是個不錯的人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.48,0:17:39.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你肯定會喜歡的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.28,0:17:52.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷轟丸之墓  做好了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.80,0:17:59.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來你也會好好做些普通的事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.12,0:18:03.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋與
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.59,0:18:18.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好球
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.49,0:18:22.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹的不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.02,0:18:25.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.90,0:18:29.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.20,0:18:33.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比呂美  你在幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.05,0:18:46.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真一郎君  你在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.40,0:19:03.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要丟下我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.98,0:19:08.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…想做什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.66,0:19:18.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}沒事吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.66,0:19:18.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比呂美  沒事吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.39,0:19:19.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.20,0:19:20.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.79,0:19:22.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比呂美  沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.98,0:19:24.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你今天有點不在狀態啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.94,0:19:26.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去休息一下比較好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.21,0:19:27.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.58,0:19:31.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧  比呂美
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.76,0:19:33.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.02,0:19:36.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  大家回到各自位置  繼續2對2練習了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.54,0:19:51.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.47,0:19:54.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,墓  是你做的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.91,0:19:55.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.16,0:20:00.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想墓還是好好地做一個比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.51,0:20:04.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我想過擅自這麼做會不會有點不好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.20,0:20:08.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正如你說的  是我把搭墓的方式弄錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.67,0:20:12.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弄錯什麼的  我不是這個意思
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.47,0:20:18.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仲上真一郎和我說了  你想和我交朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.11,0:20:21.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎…  那個
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.70,0:20:22.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是騙人的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.75,0:20:27.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你對仲上真一郎說謊了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.67,0:20:31.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說謊？  為什麼你這麼說…？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.53,0:20:34.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你不喜歡我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.91,0:20:38.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係  我沒有生氣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.06,0:20:47.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  比呂美  沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.79,0:20:51.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說  你給我等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.62,0:20:54.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了  是我不好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.80,0:20:59.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休息好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.51,0:21:00.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.11,0:21:02.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之我們先回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.94,0:21:06.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  我們馬上就回去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.08,0:21:21.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和石動乃繪談過了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.54,0:21:22.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,詳細的事我…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.46,0:21:23.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.82,0:21:26.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說不用了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.71,0:21:28.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我被石動同學拒絕了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.33,0:21:32.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她說不能和我做朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.25,0:21:35.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.67,0:21:36.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.83,0:21:38.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說了…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.75,0:21:42.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實我不是真的想和她做朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.62,0:21:44.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.75,0:21:46.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.07,0:21:51.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是  那又為什麼…？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.55,0:21:56.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是  我覺得石動同學很厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.06,0:21:58.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我被她給看透了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.67,0:23:42.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  石動乃繪？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.31,0:23:43.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人騎摩托車來接她？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.45,0:23:46.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要丟下我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.87,0:23:48.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要丟下我  真一郎君
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.93,0:23:50.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.54,0:23:53.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？  前幾天的事
